{
  "title": "AD #10 · Attracting People to Rural Areas (Path C · Design)",
  "lessons": [
    {
      "translation": "Claire 想补贴农民，Kelly 想引入商店和餐厅。",
      "phrases": ["Claire wants", "farm subsidies", "and Kelly wants", "to bring in shops", "and restaurants."],
