    {
      "translation": "真正的解法是政府先在乡村建起强公共服务——好学校、诊所、快速网络——让私人生活在上面生长。",
      "phrases": ["The real fix", "is for the government", "to set up", "strong public services", "in rural areas first —", "good schools,", "clinics,", "and fast internet —", "and let private life", "grow on top of that."],
      "zhPhrases": ["真正的解法，", "是让政府", "率先建起", "强大的公共服务", "在乡村地区——", "好学校、", "诊所，", "以及快速网络——", "再让私人生活", "在其之上生长。"]
    },
    {
      "translation": "逻辑在于顺序。",
      "phrases": ["The logic is about order."],
      "zhPhrases": ["逻辑在于顺序。"]
    },
    {
      "translation": "补贴农民只会吸引那些本来就想务农的人。",
      "phrases": ["Subsidizing farmers", "only attracts people", "who already want to farm."],
